Using the following creates a save changes button
{{{
<<saveChanges>>
}}}

Displays as:

<<saveChanges>>

The button label can also be changed and a tooltip added:
{{{
<<saveChanges [label] [tip]>>
}}}
Displays as:

<<saveChanges [label] [tip]>>